    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The return type of the function is a string or an integer that represents the meter type. The structure is a single scalar value, which be a descriptive name (e.g., \"Residential\", \"Commercial\") or a numeric code corresponding to predefined meter types."
        }
      ]
    },
